Based on the industry talk, I discovered that I-Farm is a
game-changer, in bringing a revolution in human
services. I-Farm offering a solution to the challenges of
accessing fresh veggies by letting the users grow and
monitor their own plant, making sustainable living
hands-on. Besides, this innovation simplifies life by
delivering quality produce to your door, saving time and
effort. I also find I-Farm uses smart technology for easy
veggie orders and IoT for real-time growth monitoring
which further impressed me. I-Farm as a key player in
ensuring food security, providing a local, fresh and
limited veggie source during tough times such as during
certain pandemic.
